bug.short_desc: Render problem with Separator in Menu.

long_desc.thetext: Render problem with Separator in Menu. See screen shot for more details.

Changed to a browser variant for IE6 and IE7 Quirks mode.
Fixed in trunk (r16734);
Move changes to Util.js (Thanks Sebastian for his exception)
*** Bug 1568 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***
*** Bug 1599 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***
*** Bug 1600 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***

The IE6 has a general render problem. The IE6 set a string to a empty "div" element. This element has a minimum size from the font. This makes problems when the "div" height should smaller then the font size. To fix the issue the style property "overflow:hidden" is added to the "div" element.
Comment: The browser variant is moved to the Util.js so that all decorations use the fix.
Closed all bugs already shipped with a release.
